HEADWORD: Mangcorn
<hw>Mang"corn`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>mengen</ets> to mix. See <er>Mingle</er>, and <er>Corn</er>.]</ety>
<def>A mixture of wheat and rye, or other species of grain.</def>
<mark>[Prov Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
